      <section eId="sec_51_0103">
        <num>51-0103</num>
        <heading>Allocation of moneys</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_51_0103__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>\nfor deposit in the water pollution control revolving fund established by\nsection twelve hundred eighty-five-j of the public authorities law, or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_51_0103__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>as specifically provided for in titles 3, 5, 7, 9 and 11 of this\narticle:\n  1. For preserving, enhancing, restoring and improving the quality of\nwater as set forth in title 3 of this article or in section twelve\nhundred eighty-five-j of the public authorities law and section 17-1909\nof this chapter, six hundred fifty million dollars ($650,000,000); and\n  2. For preserving, enhancing, restoring and improving the quality of\nair as set forth in title 5 of this article, one hundred fifty million\ndollars ($150,000,000); and\n  3. For preserving, enhancing, restoring and improving the quality of\nland as set forth in titles 7, 9 and 11 of this article, three hundred\nfifty million dollars ($350,000,000).\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
